@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_todbyq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.92) - 0.30))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v0 + 0.75) / 0.70))
    tmp = 0.53
    tmp = (v2 + wp.exp(v0))
    v0 = v2
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((tmp + 0.88 * v2 + 0.16)))
    v0 = (v0 * wp.abs((tmp + 0.26 * v0 + 0.85)))
    data[tid] = v0
